---
// Componente para mostrar las marcas propias de fiestas (Gamberro y La Juerga)
---

<section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-5 tracking-tight">
        Marcas <span class="text-gold-500">Propias</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-base">
        Conceptos únicos de fiesta creados, producidos y sonorizados por
        VIBE EVENTS.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Gamberro Party -->
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/gamberroparty/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group block p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/30 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all duration-500 backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-6">
          <img
            src="/gamberro.jpg"
            alt="Gamberro Party"
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 group-hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors shadow-xl"
          />
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors"
            >
              Gamberro
            </h3>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-500/80 uppercase tracking-widest"
              >Fiesta Urbana</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          La fiesta con más rebeldía de la provincia. Una atmósfera oscura,
          urbana y llena de energía enfocada en los ritmos más actuales.
        </p>
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-zinc-900 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:bg-gradient-to-tr hover:from-yellow-500 hover:via-pink-500 hover:to-purple-500 hover:border-transparent hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(236,72,153,0.4)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"
            ></rect><path
              d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"
            ></path><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"
            ></line></svg
          >
          @gamberroparty
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- La Juerga -->
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/_lajuerga_/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group block p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/30 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-500 backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-6">
          <img
            src="/lajuerga.jpg"
            alt="La Juerga"
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 group-hover:border-red-500/50 transition-colors shadow-xl"
          />
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-red-500 transition-colors"
            >
              La Juerga
            </h3>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500/80 uppercase tracking-widest"
              >Esencia Festiva</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Esencia festiva, folclore y rumbas con el toque comercial
          definitivo. La experiencia más alegre y del sur que vas a vivir.
        </p>
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-zinc-900 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:bg-gradient-to-tr hover:from-yellow-500 hover:via-pink-500 hover:to-purple-500 hover:border-transparent hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(236,72,153,0.4)] transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"
            ></rect><path
              d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"
            ></path><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"
            ></line></svg
          >
          @_lajuerga_
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
